assetProfile.address2: 1st Floor No. 16 Langshan Road North District, Science Park, Nanshan District
assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Shenzhen Newway Photomask Making Co., Ltd, a lithography company, engages in the design, development, and production of photomask products in China. The company offers large, small, and medium sized masks for applications in the fields of mask plates for TP touch screens, IC/IC bumping/IC lead frames, FPC/PCB circuit boards, BGA and HDI carrier plates, PDP/VFD, MEMS, LED, and discrete devices, as well as for display panels, such as TFT LCD, OLED, and MicroLED; OLED, EL, and display masks; color STN, STN, and TNLCD masks; masks for various optical devices and optical communications, and various encodings, as well as for fine electronic components, including chip inductors, capacitors, resistors, and sensors; other flat panel displays comprising CF; and various semiconductor integrated circuit packaging masks. It also provides mask repair and cleaning services, as well as engages in mask recycling services. The company was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Shenzhen, China.
